reviews.review_text: 1990 No question if you evaluate all the era's of the Dead 1990 was the peak, they were at their best by far. The only caveat is the sound was better during the "wall of sound" phase. 90 was some type of vortex, when all cylinders were running smooth and the band was in space overdrive. Good Vibes
